unikl.disco.numbers

Interface Num

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NaN, NegativeInfinity, PositiveInfinity, RationalBigInt, RationalInt, RealDouble, RealSingle

    public interface Num
    Class emulating multiple dispatch (Java only offers single dispatch) in order to allow the user to switch between available number representations.
    Author:
    Steffen Bondorf
